        "text": "\u201cIf you were aware,\u201d said Elizabeth, \u201cof the very great disadvantage to us all which must arise from the public notice of Lydia\u2019s unguarded and imprudent manner\u2014nay, which has already arisen from it, I am sure you would judge differently in the affair.\u201d",
